oogle.com/d/msg/fishcooking/znU1a7aZ2XI/yJDFtOQnAwAJ\">mg vs eg eval</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Joost VandeVondele</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, October 06, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Middlegame\" title=\"Middlegame\">Middlegame</a>, <a href=\"/Endgame\" title=\"Endgame\">Endgame</a>, <a href=\"/Tapered_Eval\" title=\"Tapered Eval\">Tapered Eval</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/liMe2Ho53j8/MXPfgmLtAgAJ\">Re: Stockfish contempt testing</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Joost VandeVondele</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, October 29, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Contempt_Factor\" title=\"Contempt Factor\">Contempt</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_..._2\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Joost_VandeVondele&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/nG6aqewRuSM/C5hn5hD3EwAJ\">The Maintainers They Are a-Changin'</a> by <a href=\"/Stephane_Nicolet\" title=\"Stephane Nicolet\">Stephane Nicolet</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, January 23, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/fishcooking/ZEaagbuQAoI/DDyqx7a8AgAJ\">stockfish COVID-19 strategy</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Joost VandeVondele</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">FishCooking</a>, March 15, 2020 <sup id=\"cite_ref-12\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https: